'''凱文·布萊德利·紐曼'''（{{lang-en|Kevin Bradley Newman}}，{{bd|1993年|8月4日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的游擊手，目前效力於匹茲堡海盜。紐曼就讀於[[亞利桑那大學|亞利桑那大學]]，並在[[2015年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2015年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]的第一輪被響尾蛇選走。
==職業生涯==
2015年大聯盟選秀，響尾蛇在第一輪19順位選進紐曼。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.post-gazette.com/sports/pirates/2015/06/08/Pirates-draft-shortstop-Kevin-Newman-19th-overall/stories/201506080204|title=Pirates draft shortstop Kevin Newman 19th overall|work=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette|date=June 8, 2015|access-date=June 9, 2015|archive-date=2018-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180817193504/http://www.post-gazette.com/sports/pirates/2015/06/08/Pirates-draft-shortstop-Kevin-Newman-19th-overall/stories/201506080204}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rotoworld.com/baseball/mlb/player/21039/kevin-newman|title=Kevin Newman info|work=Rotoworld|access-date=August 29, 2020|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028180727/https://www.rotoworld.com/baseball/mlb/player/21039/kevin-newman}}</ref>他和球隊後加入了短期1A，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://newsok.com/pirates-sign-top-pick-kevin-newman/article/feed/852185|title=Pirates sign top pick Kevin Newman|work=[[NewsOK.com|NewsOK.com]]|date=June 15, 2015|access-date=June 15, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323043838/http://newsok.com/pirates-sign-top-pick-kevin-newman/article/feed/852185}}</ref>並在8月升上1A。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bucsdugout.com/2015/8/9/9122355/pirates-promote-kevin-newman-to-west-virginia-power|title=Pirates promote Kevin Newman to West Virginia Power|author=Charlie Wilmoth|work=Bucs Dugout|access-date=2021-03-23|archive-date=2018-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180817225558/https://www.bucsdugout.com/2015/8/9/9122355/pirates-promote-kevin-newman-to-west-virginia-power}}</ref>這年他總共出賽61場比賽，打擊率為2成57，並敲出2轟與17分打點。2016年他升上高階1A，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20160427&content_id=174636848&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb&sid=milb |title=FSL notes: Newman's bat making noise early |publisher=MiLB.com |date=2016-04-27 |access-date=2019-10-07 |archive-date=2016-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629152640/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20160427&content_id=174636848&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb&sid=milb }}</ref>不久便升上2A。2017年季中，紐曼升上3A。整年打擊率為2成67，並敲出4轟與41分打點。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=621028#/career/R/hitting/2017/ALL|title=Kevin Newman Stats, Highlights, Bio - MiLB.com Stats - The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|publisher=MiLB.com|access-date=February 18, 2018|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125113009/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=621028#/career/R/hitting/2017/ALL}}</ref>

2018年，紐曼在小聯盟的打擊率突破3成，他也因此在8月中登上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.triblive.com/sports/pirates/13980476-85/with-jordy-mercer-out-pirates-bring-1st-round-pick-kevin-newman-to-majors|title=With Jordy Mercer out, Pirates bring 1st-round pick Kevin Newman to majors - TribLIVE.com|website=archive.triblive.com|access-date=2021-03-23|archive-date=2019-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190505202617/https://archive.triblive.com/sports/pirates/13980476-85/with-jordy-mercer-out-pirates-bring-1st-round-pick-kevin-newman-to-majors}}</ref>2019年4月6日，紐曼敲出大聯盟生涯第一支再見安打。那年他的打擊率為3成08，而他敲出國聯最多的22支內野安打，另外每8個打席就被三振一次也是國聯最高。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=bat&lg=all&qual=y&type=2&season=2019&month=0&season1=2019&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&startdate=2019-01-01&enddate=2019-12-31&sort=10,d |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2019 » Batters » Batted Ball Statistics | FanGraphs Baseball |publisher=Fangraphs.com |date=2019-01-01 |access-date=2019-10-07 |archive-date=2020-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605012238/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=bat&lg=all&qual=y&type=2&season=2019&month=0&season1=2019&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&startdate=2019-01-01&enddate=2019-12-31&sort=10,d }}</ref>
==個人生活==
紐曼目前已婚，他和他老婆Shayne在2021年1月迎來第一胎。目前他們一家現居於亞利桑那的錢德勒。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://pittsburgh.cbslocal.com/2020/07/30/kevin-newman-and-wife-shayne-announce-theyre-expecting-daughter/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-23 |archive-date=2021-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210402003323/https://pittsburgh.cbslocal.com/2020/07/30/kevin-newman-and-wife-shayne-announce-theyre-expecting-daughter/ }}</ref><ref>https://www.instagram.com/p/CGyEQ7igZwq/</ref>
